data.description: One of a kind, completely fenced 10 acres, with a pond and shop located in Newcastle. Home is 2147 square feet boasting 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and an office. The home has been completely renovated with all new flooring and trim throughout. 2400 square feet of concrete has been poured outside. There is an additional 600 square feet of space in the shop that is heated and cooled, this space also includes a half bath. If outdoor living is your thing, this place has it with multiple areas for seating as well as a covered gazebo for those nice Oklahoma evenings!
